\subsubsection parameters ROS parameters

Reads and maintains the following parameters on the ROS server

- \b "~slowdown_distance" : \b [double] distance at which the robot starts slowing down min: 0.0, default: 5.0, max: 20.0
- \b "~danger_threshold" : \b [double] threshold at which warning signal is being published min: 0.0, default: 0.6, max: 1.0

